c Chain of Thought Prompting in Large Language Models\",\n        \"year\": 2022,\n        \"citations\": 891,\n        \"url\": \"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/90350aa626bed47b02d0c162462e5b0ca82be6b2\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"title\": \"Language Models Don't Always Say What They Think: Unfaithful Explanations in Chain-of-Thought Prompting\",\n        \"year\": 2023,\n        \"citations\": 835,\n        \"url\": \"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/7dc928f41e15f65f1267bd87b0fcfcc7e715cb56\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"title\": \"Self-Consistency Improves Chain of Thought Reasoning in Language Models\",\n        \"year\": 2022,\n        \"citations\": 6008,\n        \"url\": \"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/5f19ae1135a9500940978104ec15a5b8751bc7d2\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"title\": \"BadChain: Backdoor Chain-of-Thought Prompting for Large Language Models\",\n        \"year\": 2024,\n        \"citations\": 85,\n        \"url\": \"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/f8d7b0245480646abd257bac60ee37804981a0d7\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"query\": \"think before you speak language models inner monologue\",\n    \"status\": 429,\n    \"results\": []\n  },\n  {\n    \"query\": \"quiet-star think before speaking\",\n    \"status\": 429,\n    \"results\": []\n  }\n]\n\nPWC: [\n  {\n    \"query\": \"chain of thought\",\n    \"url\": \"https://paperswithcode.com/search?q=chain%20of%20thought\",\n    \"status\": 200,\n    \"title_present\": true\n  },\n  {\n    \"query\": \"tree of thoughts\",\n    \"url\": \"https://paperswithcode.com/search?q=tree%20of%20thoughts\",\n    \"status\": 200,\n    \"title_present\": true\n  },\n  {\n    \"query\": \"truthfulqa\",\n    \"url\": \"https://paperswithcode.com/search?q=truthfulqa\",\n    \"status\": 200,\n    \"title_present\": true\n  }\n]\n-rw-r--r-- 1 19173 22600  460 Mar  1 04:39 paperswithcode_search.json\n-rw-r--r-- 1 19173 22600 1.6K Mar  1 04:39 semantic_scholar_search.json\n","exit_code